io.proximax.sdk.model.transaction.builder

Class TransactionBuilder<B extends TransactionBuilder<B,T>,T extends Transaction>

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.proximax.sdk.model.transaction.builder.TransactionBuilder<B,T>
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AccountLinkTransactionBuilder, AggregateTransactionBuilder, AliasTransactionBuilder, BlockchainConfigTransactionBuilder, BlockchainUpgradeTransactionBuilder, LockFundsTransactionBuilder, ModifyAccountPropertyTransactionBuilder, ModifyContractTransactionBuilder, ModifyMetadataTransactionBuilder, ModifyMultisigAccountTransactionBuilder, MosaicDefinitionTransactionBuilder, MosaicSupplyChangeTransactionBuilder, RegisterNamespaceTransactionBuilder, SecretLockTransactionBuilder, SecretProofTransactionBuilder, TransferTransactionBuilder

    public abstract class TransactionBuilder<B extends TransactionBuilder<B,T>,T extends Transaction>
extends java.lang.Object
    Transaction builder is base class implementing builder pattern to construct instance of transaction. It is bases of specialized transaction builders for all types of transactions
